column2: SELECT TOP A specObjID, survey, bestobjid, z /*Table of top A random objects with redshift, survey they are in, and object ID for searching*/ FROM SpecObj /*Objects with spectra*/ WHERE class = # /* The objects shown will all be QSO#sdss#boss') /*searching across both the legacy and boss surveys (and not other surveys) */ order by newid () /* This is the randomisation algorithm */
